{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1016847, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "《走向imo》", "timestamp": 1611969121, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1016866, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "走向ipho", "timestamp": 1611969514, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1016873, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 谢谢～", "timestamp": 1611969594, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1016901, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "物理学难题集萃", "timestamp": 1611970473, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1016960, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "物理我不清楚\n数学:小蓝书 奥赛经典 命题人讲座等系列\n走向imo是真题，可以了解之前各个竞赛的题目", "timestamp": 1611971529, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1016972, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 小蓝书，又名数学奥林匹克小丛书", "timestamp": 1611971661, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1017048, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 物理错题集萃", "timestamp": 1611972855, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1017177, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "呃呃，正经地回答一下，，\n物理竞赛入门：程书力学、电磁学；比程书简单但是技巧性强的是黑白皮（新编物理学竞赛啥啥，真的记不清名字）；更简单的是绿皮。个人推荐程书，经典中的经典。光学、热学、近代物理部分自求多福，我没见过很好的书，不妨直接去刷往年竞赛题（崔宏斌有一本书，但质量简直不能再差）。\n进阶：刷往届题（很多资料都难以把握练习题的尺度，因为题大多非原创，或者随便想了个题）；江四喜的书（新出的，质量不错）；舒幼生力学教材；中科大电磁学教材、赵凯华新概念物理教材等；\n再进阶：物理学难题集萃（有的题太数学，严格来讲难集是本科生读物，甚至被标为考研书）；国培（没做过不知道）；这个层面就要读一点大学教材了", "timestamp": 1611974519, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1017263, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "理论力学，热力学，电动力学，量子力学", "timestamp": 1611975700, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1017513, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 国培和新概念都没那么进阶，程书其实也没那么初阶。。。\n", "timestamp": 1611979036, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1018790, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 随手分类嘛，没那么准，，", "timestamp": 1611992542, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1018871, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 还有 奥赛物理题选+奥赛物理试题选 隔壁出版社的", "timestamp": 1611993651, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019151, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 还有俄五百！yyds", "timestamp": 1611996707, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019286, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "ssfd.jpg", "timestamp": 1611998320, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 202562, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "求问万洞现在学物理和数学竞赛用哪本书比较好？", "timestamp": 1611969105, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1611998321, "url": "", "vote": {}}}